{"tid":1452624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[極重要][戰術回顧]811前線要知的細節位，究竟點解去咗銅鑼灣","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T00:19:23.000Z","uid":79046,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b3de2f322fc14b810541779c20df612d18cacf3e","tid":1452624,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"深水埗射完催淚彈後，前線話要開小組討論，討論去向，有人話銅鑼灣有前線做野，要幫拖（當時銅鑼灣只係和平集會，無衝突發生），有人話去尖沙咀，又有人話去灣仔，於是就分咗批。<br />\n<br />\n小妹睇住直播嗰位記者就跟咗去銅鑼灣，但見到無事，於是又開始小組討論，多次討論拖延咗好多時間，途中有人不斷話要北角，而眾所周知北角重防+福建佬，而嗰啲人不斷話北角有前線手足，但有巴打重覆確認咗北角無戰友，於是嗰啲人就轉口，話不如都係照守銅鑼灣啦！<br />\n<br />\n因為灣仔嗰邊有手足過緊來，所以留在銅鑼灣守住先。過咗一陣，真係有一班手足過咗來。之後有7人車速龍想撞埋來，大家一齊退，所以營造咗大家都係戰友的感覺，速龍失敗後，大家繼續開小組討論，決定留守銅鑼灣。<br />\n<br />\n再夜啲，速龍再衝，然後大家會以為又會一齊退啦，就發生手足背叛事件，其中有份參與的鬼，有兩種。<br />\n1. 身上無所謂的單邊耳機、綠光筆，係正常齊裝衝擊手的look，有參與深水埗小組討論，一直有跟住大家。<br />\n2. 後來灣仔加入，身上裝備齊全，都無單邊耳機，氣勢高昂好想衝。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點：<br />\n1. 堅持自己有手足在警察重防地點，引大家過去或者附近的地點。<br />\n2. 希望大家一齊去，拉大隊一齊去，有指揮的feel。<br />\n3. 各Gamer自己要有情報確認的方法，例如搵朋友mon住哨兵group及各傳媒直播，幫你極速整理出重點情報，你一問，佢1分鐘內答得出所在地點的情況。最好嗰位朋友有方法在安全情況下到該地點拍攝一手情報，以供在場巴絲參考。<br />\n4. 佢地無任何標記物，只會在背叛完的前後戴上，所以無法預先捉鬼；而預先捉鬼有機會捉錯人影響士氣，所以依然唔好即場割蓆，唯有靠自己保自己後路。<br />\n5. 見到好多前線唔信情報，所以最好用返第3點的方法，咁唔洗自己思考現場戰友的情報真偽。<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n不割蓆，核彈都唔割<br />\n不分化<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不指揮<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n雙普選前<br />\n誓不罷休"},{"pid":"1f01e0ea7bbe8a771adc10c3ddaf4fd19f79113f","tid":1452624,"uid":32719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RntuKxi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRntuKxi.jpg&h=2d720f36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNktfDZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNktfDZ.jpg&h=5d6abd42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gk0wXSn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk0wXSn.jpg&h=b2d98c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dV4xHi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdV4xHi5.jpg&h=8aeecf39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrKE6LM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrKE6LM.png&h=b9706757&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DL2GAD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDL2GAD7.png&h=2d6e2c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARU9Kxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARU9Kxu.png&h=a32d7290&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ki2Wpxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fki2Wpxw.jpg&h=ad0dcc4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LEuNwcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLEuNwcz.jpg&h=ea6c9a69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHnjnjf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHnjnjf.png&h=694880f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ff85b8e49433856b928e758aa2af4932cbc6919","tid":1452624,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:23.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"cc915a7b56fe9a6ca39ef5ee4e5bbaa21dadee42","tid":1452624,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:33.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"58ff1651fb0ce100a83d573f0818e546fa807dd6","tid":1452624,"uid":281418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"097f821e86cc74c8fb9497fc3198d1980be284fc","tid":1452624,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:44.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"7107a78682536acab1244f6f95816170cb0333fa","tid":1452624,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:54.000Z","msg":"3"}